        "content": "<p>It looks like the Micromodal migration resulted in regression where the buttons don't look right in dark theme:<br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/2/80/KRwJQltvhkNURhtlJ7NQf__N/Screen-Shot-2021-12-03-at-5.51.04-PM.png\">Screen-Shot-2021-12-03-at-5.51.04-PM.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/2/80/KRwJQltvhkNURhtlJ7NQf__N/Screen-Shot-2021-12-03-at-5.51.04-PM.png\" title=\"Screen-Shot-2021-12-03-at-5.51.04-PM.png\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/2/80/KRwJQltvhkNURhtlJ7NQf__N/Screen-Shot-2021-12-03-at-5.51.04-PM.png\"></a></div><p>Compare to prior to the migration:<br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/2/af/w8utMvUAJkAaKgTn9WRWUs8x/Screen-Shot-2021-12-03-at-5.50.30-PM.png\">Screen-Shot-2021-12-03-at-5.50.30-PM.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/2/af/w8utMvUAJkAaKgTn9WRWUs8x/Screen-Shot-2021-12-03-at-5.50.30-PM.png\" title=\"Screen-Shot-2021-12-03-at-5.50.30-PM.png\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/2/af/w8utMvUAJkAaKgTn9WRWUs8x/Screen-Shot-2021-12-03-at-5.50.30-PM.png\"></a></div><p>How do folks think these buttons <em>should</em> look? Roughly the same as before?</p>",
        "id": 1291368,
