        "timestamp": 1638583068
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I think those buttons are fancier buttons than the settings menu buttons.  However, I'd be content with us reverting the modals to use the buttons we had before, which we also use in the settings menus.  It's possible we'll want to then do a redesign for the buttons we use in menus, but it seems like that sort of design update process would be made substantially simpler by not having this as an extra parallel button set to manage.</p>",
        "id": 1291376,
        "sender_full_name": "Tim Abbott",
        "timestamp": 1638583288
    },
    {
